OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef was in court for the
OL,9,Fsentencing of Robert Easom
OL,11,FA "violent and controlling bully" who
OL,12,Fleft his partner paralysed after
OL,13,Fsevering her spinal cord in a brutal
OL,14,Fattack when she told him she was
OL,15,Fleaving him, has been jailed for 16
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
