PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FRobert Easom, 56, subjected his
OL,8,Fpartner of eight years Trudi Burgess
OL,9,Fto a campaign of coercive and
OL,10,Fcontrolling behaviour, regularly
OL,11,Fverbally abusing her and - at times -
OL,12,Fphysically assaulting her.
OL,14,FHis catalogue of abuse included
OL,15,Fforcing her to clean up spilled food,
OL,16,Fpushing her against furniture,
OL,17,Fshouting at her, driving dangerously
OL,18,Fto frighten her, and headbutting her,
OL,19,Fa court was told.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIt came to a horrific climax on 17
OL,8,FFebruary 2025 where, after telling
OL,9,FEasom she was leaving, Trudi was
OL,10,Fbrutally assaulted, severing her
OL,11,Fspinal cord and leaving her paralysed
OL,12,Fand requiring specialist care.
OL,14,FJudge Robert Altham sentencing Easom
OL,16,FAfter a trial at Preston Crown Court
OL,17,FEasom was found guilty of Section 18
OL,18,Fwounding with intent - the most
OL,19,Fserious forms of assault.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe had previously admitted to engaging
OL,8,Fin coercive and controlling behaviour
OL,9,Fbetween July 2017 and February 2025,
OL,10,Fas well as two offences of actual
OL,11,Fbodily harm.
OL,13,FJailing him for 16 years with an
OL,14,Fadditional four years on licence,
OL,15,FJudge Robert Altham said "no sentence
OL,16,FI can pass can begin to equal the harm
OL,17,Fwhich you have caused".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FHe added: "Even with the lengthy
OL,8,Fsentence I am about to impose you will
OL,9,Fhave the prospect of a future which
OL,10,Fyou have denied your victim."
OL,12,FIn a powerful victim impact statement
OL,13,FTrudi told the court of Easom's
OL,14,F"Jekyll and Hyde personality", adding
OL,15,Fwhile he could be "a loving and
OL,16,Fattentive partner... he could switch
OL,17,Fin a moment into a truly terrifying
OL,18,Fmonster".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FDescribing the impact the attack has
OL,8,Fhad on her, she told the court:
OL,9,F"Emotionally I have been shattered. I
OL,10,Fgrieve every day for the life I've
OL,11,Flost - a life that was stolen from me
OL,12,Fby someone who I trusted. I feel
OL,13,Ftrapped and powerless.
OL,15,F"Sometimes I feel like I'm just
OL,16,Fsurviving... not living. Everything
OL,17,Fthat once gave me joy now feels out of
OL,18,Freach.
OL,20,F"My future has been rewritten and not
OL,21,Fby choice."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FTrudi answered police questions from
OL,8,Fher hospital bed - nodding or shaking
OL,9,Fher head in reply
OL,11,FShe added: "My children and
OL,12,Fgranddaughter have lost the mother and
OL,13,Fgrandmother they once had. And I am
OL,14,Fleft learning to live a life I didn't
OL,15,Fchoose ` and would not wish on anyone.
OL,17,F"This isn't just a physical injury, it
OL,18,Fis the destruction of a life. And the
OL,19,Fpain doesn't stop with me ` the
OL,20,Fripples of pain are felt by everyone
OL,21,Fwho loves me and cares for me.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"I want the court to consider not just
OL,8,Fthe brutality of the attack but the
OL,9,Fongoing permanent consequences I now
OL,10,Fface - every minute of every day - for
OL,11,Fthe rest of my life."
OL,13,FThe pair had met after Trudi's husband
OL,14,Fdied from brain cancer, and Easom was
OL,15,Fworking as a landscape gardener for
OL,16,Fher sister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FDuring his trial at Preston Crown
OL,8,FCourt jurors heard how at first he was
OL,9,Fthe "perfect partner" but the mother
OL,10,Fof two soon became trapped in a
OL,11,Fvicious cycle of abuse.
OL,13,FThroughout her relationship Trudi
OL,14,Fdocumented the abuse she received in
OL,15,Fthe notes section of her phone.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FAlongside the serious physical
OL,8,Fassaults she also described what she
OL,9,Fcalled "low-level events" which became
OL,10,Fnormalised - living in a cycle in
OL,11,Fwhich Easom would be verbally or
OL,12,Fphysically abusive then apologetic and
OL,13,Faffectionate.
OL,15,FAround seven months into the
OL,16,Frelationship, during a trip to York,
OL,17,FLancashire Police said Easom
OL,18,F"switched" into a rage, dragging her
OL,19,Faround the bathroom, threatening her
OL,20,Fand quoting a line from Rambo "Don't
OL,21,Fpush or I'll give you a war."
OL,26,@|D@_OU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FWhen she tried to leave, the force
OL,8,Fadded, he begged her to stay and acted
OL,9,Fremorseful.
OL,11,FRobert Easom lied to 999 call
OL,12,Foperators about attacking Trudi
OL,14,FIn another incident in 2019, Easom
OL,15,Fviolently grabbed her wine, slammed a
OL,16,Ffridge door, and shouted before
OL,17,Fdragging her upstairs by the head,
OL,18,Fbanging her against each step.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIn 2021, again in York, he placed a
OL,8,Fsheet over her head and strangled her,
OL,9,Fleaving her terrified for her life.
OL,10,FThe next day, he dismissed the attack,
OL,11,Fclaiming he was "just trying to teach
OL,12,Fher a lesson".
OL,14,FDespite knowing she needed to leave,
OL,15,FTrudi says she became trapped in a
OL,16,Fcycle of abuse, with Easom belittling
OL,17,Fher, telling her she was "useless" and
OL,18,Fcould not cope without him.
OL,26,@sD@QOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FOvertime, police said, her self-esteem
OL,8,Fwas eroded, leaving her "confused and
OL,9,Fbroken down" - although she continued
OL,10,Fto record notes "as a way to make
OL,11,Fsense of what was happening".
OL,13,FSpeaking outside court, Trudi thanked
OL,14,Fher family, friends and medical
OL,15,Fprofessionals who supported her
OL,16,Frecovery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772309090
OL,3,C'Violent and controlling bully' jailed
OL,4,Cafter paralysing partner in brutal
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FShe said: "I feel very sad. But I feel
OL,8,Fcontent that justice has been done.
OL,9,FBut it's not a happy day because I'm
OL,10,Flike this for the rest of my life, and
OL,11,Fthis is an incredibly difficult
OL,12,Fcondition to be in.
OL,14,F"When I glanced over at him, I just
OL,15,Ffelt sad and pity and complete sorrow
OL,16,Fthat he can't understand who he is and
OL,17,Fthe rehabilitation that he needs that
OL,18,FI didn't recognise."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
